   1373          /**
   1374           *    @brief    This method writes one byte of data into the Uart transmitter FIFO.
   1375           *    @details  The data in the Transmitter FIFO is sent to other Uart node through the specified Uart COM port\n
   1376           *              whenever the Transmitter is free.\n
